 Removing Harm from Roads","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Clearing harmful things from the road is charity.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20522,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/al-mundhiri-none-favored-but-righteousness\/","url_meta":{"origin":14519,"position":3},"title":"Imam al-Mundhiri on None Favored but by Righteousness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\"It is enough evil to look down upon his brother.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14427,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/islam-against-racism-bigotry\/","url_meta":{"origin":14519,"position":4},"title":"Islam is against racism and prejudice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Verily, the most noble of you to Allah is the most righteous of you.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0625\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14792,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/an-nawawi-friday-prayer-jumuah-jummah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14519,"position":5},"title":"Imam al-Nawawi on Friday Prayer, Salat al-Jumu&#8217;ah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"\"Verily, the best of your days is Friday.\"","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Hadith Chapters \u0623\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u062f\u064a\u062b","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/category\/hadith-chapters\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14519","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=14519"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14519\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=14519"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=14519"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=14519"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}